io.sphere.sdk.carts

Interface CartLike<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of this CartLike, order or cart
    All Superinterfaces:
    CreationTimestamped, Custom, Identifiable<T>, Referenceable<T>, Resource<T>, ResourceIdentifiable<T>, ResourceView<T,T>, Timestamped, Versioned<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Cart, Order

    public interface CartLike<T>
extends Resource<T>, Custom
    Interface to collect the common stuff between carts and orders.

    If you want to use this class as abstraction for Cart and Order then use it as CartLike<?>.

      • calculateSubTotalPrice

        default javax.money.MonetaryAmount calculateSubTotalPrice()
        Returns the subtotal price of the cart, which is calculated by adding the prices of line items and custom line items, thus excluding shipping costs and discounts that are applied to the entire cart.

      • calculateTotalAppliedTaxes

        default Optional<javax.money.MonetaryAmount> calculateTotalAppliedTaxes()
        Tries to calculate all the taxes applied to the cart, without discriminating between different tax portions. Only possible if taxes have already been applied to the cart.
        Returns:
        the taxes applied to the cart, or absent if taxes have not been applied yet
